outputs.output_descr: As recommended by the Country Programme Mid-Term Review exercise conducted in mid 2005, strengthening national counterparts' capacities in UNDP programming using NEX, financial procedures and reporting is essential. To this end, a number of workshops, seminars and meetings will be organized to meet these needs ultimately ensuring effective and efficient implementation of UNDP Nationally Executed (NEX) projects in Jordan

project_descr: Umbrella Project to Support the UNDP Programme Development and Implementation in Jordan
project_title: Supp the UNDP Programme Dev & Implementation in Jordan
